text: "Venom" is a hip-hop song by American rapper Eminem, released on September 21, 2018. It was written for the soundtrack of the 2018 movie of the same name and featured in his tenth studio album, Kamikaze. Comercially, It reached the top 10 in Czechia,http://hitparada.ifpicr.cz/index.php?hitp=D Greece, Hungary, and Slovakia.http://hitparada.ifpicr.cz/index.php?hitp=D ==References== Category:2018 songs Category:Eminem songs Category:Venom (movie series)
